T1  - A Model for the Determination of “Fair” Premiums on Lease Cancellation Insurance Policies
AU  - SCHALLHEIM, JAMES S.
AU  - McCONNELL, JOHN J.
Y1  - 1985/12/01
PY  - 1985
DA  - 1985/12/01
